{
  "texts": [
    "Students must not reference materials that they have not read.",
    "As a report author, the student is accountable for the work that they produce, this accountability cannot apply to an LLM (Nature, 2023).",
    "This research reinforces the significance of SoTL in guiding educational practices in the age of AI-assisted writing.",
    "The article employs a SoTL approach by systematically investigating the use of ChatGPT in HE, reflecting on teaching practices, involving students and faculty in the research, and sharing the results to inform and improve teaching and learning.",
    "This revealed that, whilst AI can provide valuable insights and aid academic writing, and it can be very difficult to confidently detect, it cannot replace academic integrity of criticality."
  ]
}